cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with recognizing surgical activities using sensors and signals. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses designing a new generation of operating rooms. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the study uses deep learning for activity recognition. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the study involves developing smart and situation-aware assistance for the operating room. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the study aims to improve surgical practices and design new operating rooms.
